BuildGoal
/ Builds a single goal - single LLM pass
/ LLM sees entire goal + compact action summary with DTOs
/ Returns complete [{module, action, parameters}] for all steps
/ Falls back to BuildStep for steps with level medium or low

- write out "Building goal: %goal.Name%"
- builder.actions, write to %actions%
- builder.types, write to %typeInfo%
- render template "/system/actions/v2/summary.md", write to %actionSummary%
- render template "/system/builder/templates/v2/goalFormatForLlm.template", write to %goalForLlm%
- read file "llm/BuildGoal.llm", load vars, write to %buildGoalPrompt%
- llm.query system=%buildGoalPrompt%, user=%goalForLlm%, scheme={description: string, errors?: [{key: string, message: string}], warnings?: [{key: string, message: string}], steps: [{index: int, guidance: string, actions?: [{module: string, action: string, parameters?: [{name: string, value?: object, type?: string}], errors?: [{key: string, message: string}], warnings?: [{key: string, message: string}]}], errors?: [{key: string, message: string}], warnings?: [{key: string, message: string}], cache?: {durationMs: long, sliding?: bool, key?: string}, onError?: {ignoreError?: bool, goal?: {name: string}, retryCount?: int, retryOverMs?: int, order?: string, message?: string}, level: string, confidence: int}]}, on error HandleBuildGoalFailure, write to %stepResults%
- call ValidateBuildResponse, on error call LlmFixer
- set %traceId% = %Now.Ticks%_%goal.Name%
- set %trace% = {id: %traceId%, goal: %goal.Name%, timestamp: %Now%, pass1: {system: %buildGoalPrompt%, user: %goalForLlm%, response: %stepResults%}, detailPasses: []}
- group %stepResults.steps% by "level", write to %groupedSteps%
- loop.foreach %groupedSteps%, goal.call ProcessGroup item=%group%
- save %trace% to file '/.build/traces/%traceId%.json'
- add %traceId% to %traceGoals%
- set %goal.Version% = "0.2.1"
- call SaveGoal %goal%


ProcessGroup
/ Process a group of steps with the same confidence level
- if %group.steps[0].level% is "low" or "medium"
    - foreach %group.steps%, call BuildStep item=%stepResult%
- foreach %group.steps%, call ApplyStep item=%stepResult%


LlmFixer
/ LLM produced invalid output — retry with error context
- write out "  Validation failed: %!error.Message% — retrying..."
- llm.query system=%buildGoalPrompt%, user="Your previous response had an error: %!error.Message%. The developer's PLang code is:\n%goalForLlm%\n\nYour previous answer:\n%stepResults%\n\nFix the error and return the correct response.", scheme={description: string, errors?: [{key: string, message: string}], warnings?: [{key: string, message: string}], steps: [{index: int, guidance: string, actions?: [{module: string, action: string, parameters?: [{name: string, value?: object, type?: string}], errors?: [{key: string, message: string}], warnings?: [{key: string, message: string}]}], errors?: [{key: string, message: string}], warnings?: [{key: string, message: string}], cache?: {durationMs: long, sliding?: bool, key?: string}, onError?: {ignoreError?: bool, goal?: {name: string}, retryCount?: int, retryOverMs?: int, order?: string, message?: string}, level: string, confidence: int}]}, write to %stepResults%
- call ValidateBuildResponse


HandleBuildGoalFailure
- write out "  Build error: %!error.Message%"
- throw %!error%